            <div class="quality">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.7.1 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.--><path d="M408 120c0 54.6-73.1 151.9-105.2 192c-7.7 9.6-22 9.6-29.6 0C241.1 271.9 168 174.6 168 120C168 53.7 221.7 0 288 0s120 53.7 120 120zm8 80.4c3.5-6.9 6.7-13.8 9.6-20.6c.5-1.2 1-2.5 1.5-3.7l116-46.4C558.9 123.4 576 135 576 152l0 270.8c0 9.8-6 18.6-15.1 22.3L416 503l0-302.6zM137.6 138.3c2.4 14.1 7.2 28.3 12.8 41.5c2.9 6.8 6.1 13.7 9.6 20.6l0 251.4L32.9 502.7C17.1 509 0 497.4 0 480.4L0 209.6c0-9.8 6-18.6 15.1-22.3l122.6-49zM327.8 332c13.9-17.4 35.7-45.7 56.2-77l0 249.3L192 449.4 192 255c20.5 31.3 42.3 59.6 56.2 77c20.5 25.6 59.1 25.6 79.6 0zM288 152a40 40 0 1 0 0-80 40 40 0 1 0 0 80z"/></svg>
              <p>Livraison partout en Europe</p>
